description: On the occasion of #OBJKT4OBJKT2 here s the first test of a new framed serie that will be specially developped for the H=N format. Some joyful, cute gifs, with that feeling of tiny autonomnous lifes forms. I will publish the serie on a new dedicated page, this one being more for experimentations and uniques pieces. Thx to the #OBJKT4OBJKT team and all the H=N freefolks !
